# This file is intentionally comment-only.
#
# `uv` 0.11.x rejects project dependency sources inside `uv.toml`; the old
# `[sources]` pattern no longer works here. Keep this example as a reminder that
# local config belongs here, but project dependency source overrides do not.
#
# If you are developing this repo alongside `../agentao`, use:
#
#   uv sync
#   uv pip install --editable ../agentao
#
# That keeps `pyproject.toml` and `uv.lock` on the published PyPI dependency
# while letting your current virtualenv import the sibling checkout.
